{
  "stem": "3928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the people came in to open another television station, an NBC station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had no television background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they came to WQED to learn something television.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I worked with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they get to know me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when they'd opened the station, they offered me a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went there and worked with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the next year, the Hearst Corporation opened a station there, WTAE-Television.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They offered me a job with more money, so I worked there as a television, news, and documentary photographer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And afterwards, I was exclusively with them a sports-- sports photographer for WTAE-Television.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then, in 1969, you know, '68, '69, I got a call from the Pittsburgh Steeler's President, Dan Rooney, want to know if I want to work for the Pittsburgh Steelers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said, I just hired a new coach, Chuck Noll, and we would like to have if you be our coaching photographer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the same day, I got a call from Joe L.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Brown, who was, at the time, the general manager of the Pittsburgh Pirates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, Les, I want you to work for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I told him, Joe, I just got a call from Danny Rooney.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He said, I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I talked to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You can work for both of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We make arrangement.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I worked for them until 1976, I worked for the Pirates and Steelers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, here is a World Series ring that prove it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This, the 1971 World Series ring, which I earned with the Pirates, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and in 1976, you know, when Jackie Sherrill became the head coach of the Pittsburgh, University of Pittsburgh football team, he heard about me.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
